**3️⃣  Portfolio Ranking (Score 0‑10)**  

Scoring methodology (max 10 points):

| Criterion | Weight | Rating scale |
|-----------|--------|--------------|
| **Moving‑Average (MA) trend** (30‑/60‑/200‑day) | 3 pts | 3 = price > 200‑day MA & trending up, 2 = above 60‑day MA, 1 = above 30‑day MA only, 0 = below 30‑day MA |
| **RSI** | 3 pts | 3 = oversold (≤30) **or** moderate (35‑45) with bullish divergence, 2 = 40‑60 neutral, 1 = 61‑70 slight overbought, 0 = >70 |
| **MACD** | 2 pts | 2 = bullish crossover in last 7 days, 1 = flat/near‑zero, 0 = bearish |
| **Volume** (Kraken 30‑day avg) | 2 pts | 2 = high (> €5 M/day), 1 = moderate (€1‑5 M), 0 = low (< €1 M) |

Score = sum of the four sub‑scores (max 10).  Comments summarise the technical picture and the recommended action (Hold / Reduce / Sell).

